{
  "texts": [
    "The task was the following: › Step 1: Analyse the social media datasets to investigate the propaganda strategies of the assigned party (30 Min)",
    "1 Cheatsheet available at: https://propaganda.",
    "qcri.org/annotations/definitions.html.",
    "› Step 2: Complete Qualtrics questionnaire 1 (15 min) › Step 3: Play with Botlitica asking questions to the assigned party (different from the one in step 1) (30 Min) › Step 4: Complete Qualtrics questionnaire 2 (15 min) In such a way we obtained a test group of 18 answers (6 per political party) after having used Botlitica (from now on TG) and a control group of 18 answers gathered from the standard data analysis of published official propaganda messages (from now on CG).",
    "For comparison purposes, the 5 questions in Questionnaire 1 and 2 were the same: Q1: What party are you evaluating?"
  ]
}